originalText.text: My twins (Alex & Sandra) went to this school for two years. They were in separate classes so I met different teaches from school. All of them are giving so much attention and afford to kids. We got huge progress in their development and even daycare teacher was asking references for their kids, seeing all that development progress what we got from Birch School. I'm so grateful for my twins to be there. All the staff is like a family for kids. Thank you for Birch Team, I wish we could stay for all grades with you. If anyone needs more details, you are more than welcome to contact me.

originalText.text: Una de las mejores escuelas donde mi hija ha estudiado, ella tuvo una linda experiencia. El profesor y las asistentes fueron muy amorosos y profesionales. Esto fue hace muchos años no se si están las mismas personas pero espero algún día regresar para que mi hija visite a sus antiguos maestros.

text.text: One of the best schools where my daughter has studied, she had a nice experience. The teacher and assistants were very loving and professional. This was many years ago, I don't know if the same people are there, but I hope one day to return so my daughter can visit her old teachers.
